ReadMe

1. /yahoo/yahoo/spiders/yahoo_spider.py is the code of main spider.
	If you want to change the logic or data you want to collect, you can change code there.
2. items.py file is like directory in Python, it can be used to store data which we download from the website.
3. If you want to change the keywords of website, you can change the "keywords = xx+xx+..." at yahoo_spider.py.
4. If you want to use this crawler, you can open a terminal and enter "scrapy crawl yahoo".


